    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small marine gastropod that flourishes in the Indian Ocean, having a porcelain-like shell that is used as money in some parts of Africa and Southern Asia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
